----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Note: this example requires GHC 7.8 to run.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

First install HERMIT version 1.0.0.0, which can be done via Cabal:

> cabal update
> cabal install hermit-1.0.0.0

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To run the example, invoke HERMIT as follows:

> hermit MapFusion.hs MapFusion.hec

If it runs successfully, you can use the HERMIT command "show-lemmas" to display the map-fusion lemma
(which should be noted as proved).

hermit> show-lemmas

To get a feel for HERMIT, try running the example without loading the script:

> hermit MapFusion.hs

And then type in the commands from the HERMIT script "MapFusion.hec" one by one.  Note that lines starting
"--" are comments, not HERMIT commands.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
